message.body: Hey lady, what's your schedule looking like for tomorrow? When are you going to Shooters? Lemme know when you can and I'll come pick up DVDs. Thanks!
Hey!! I went today after work. Tape looks great! I'll be free after 12 tomorrow so anytime after that!
Awesome! I'm glad you got it done and that it looks great. I have to be in Center city at 6. Is it cool if I come by around 5 or so?
I can come earlier if you need me to.
Please shoot me your new address.
I am running a little behind. I will be at your house around 5:30.
No prob bob. If there's no parking, just double park and I'll run out to you!
Awesome. Thanks! I'll let you know when I get there.
I'm at your house... "Now give me back my phone..."
